   <abstract>Recto shows Slim Clarke smiling and presumably holding a guitar. Recto reads: Yodelin' Slim Clarke Wheeling Records. Verso reads: Dear Mom and All: Hope all are well. Will be Home on the 30th. Have Marion snap on the furnace Thermostat and just leave it. Just make sure it comes on. Do it in the morning so it will be warm. See you Later. Love Slim and all. Addressed to Ms. Mary A. Clarke.</abstract>
